'''肋棘海林檎'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Pleurocystes'''''}}）是生存在[[奧陶紀|奧陶紀]]的一種[[海林檎|海林檎]]，其[[化石|化石]]分布於全世界。牠們具有扁平的[[三角形|三角形]]萼，其後部邊緣為最寬處，向前部呈錐狀縮小。柄由許多短小、帶有脊骨的柱組成。下部表層小骨板的拼組式覆蓋物是最主要的。肋棘海林檎生活在海底，身體的下部埋於沉積物中，用節盤繞於柄的基層上。<ref>{{cite book | title=自然珍藏系列──化石圖鑑 | location = [[台灣|台灣]][[新北市|新北市]] | publisher=[[貓頭鷹出版社|貓頭鷹出版社]] | author= Cyril Walker | author2= Davod Ward | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=自然珍藏系列 | year=2002 | page=191 | date = 2002-02 | language = zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title=Fossils | url=https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0 | publisher=[[Dorling_Kindersley|Dorling Kindersley]] | author=Walker, Cyril | last2=Ward | first2=David | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=Smithsonian Handbooks | year=2002 | page=[https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0/page/191 191] | isbn=0789489848 | edition=revised, illustrated}}</ref>

